    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>greens</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min further</p><p>Add the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add <strong>half </strong>your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and mash everything together, then flatten the mixture out in the pan</p><p>Increase the heat to high and cook for 3-4 min or until the bottom is starting to crisp</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1582200419863-x200.jpg",
