            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Give the <strong>potato & vegetable mixture</strong> a good mix up to stir through the crispy base</p><p>Roughly re-flatten the mixture in the pan and sprinkle over the <strong>grated cheese </strong>and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Put the pan under the grill for 4-5 min or until the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>cheesy bubble & squeak</strong></p><p>Tip: Make sure you leave the pan handle outside of the oven and the door open whilst grilling!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1582200430242-x200.jpg",
